column1: Crowdsourced data on dried cannabis expenditure, prices and use.
The application was launched January 25, 2018. Data are being collected continuously and will be made available as new information comes in.
All submissions are reported below, however, the associated Daily is based on the information without any outlier (Outlier = 0).
Statistics Canada applies a set of criteria on the price variable to determine whether a submission is an outlier (Outlier =1).
